Package com.opengamma.strata.basics

Interface ReferenceDataId<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the reference data this identifier refers to
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EtdContractSpecId, HolidayCalendarId, LegalEntityId, SecurityId, TestingReferenceDataId
    public interface ReferenceDataId<T>
    An identifier for a unique item of reference data.

    Reference data is obtained from an instance of ReferenceData using this identifier.

      • queryValueOrNull

        default T queryValueOrNull​(ReferenceData refData)
        Low-level method to query the reference data value associated with this identifier, returning null if not found.

        This is a low-level method that obtains the reference data value, returning null instead of an error. Applications should use ReferenceData.getValue(ReferenceDataId) in preference to this method.

        Parameters:
        refData - the reference data to lookup the value in
        Returns:
        the reference data value, null if not found
